data.description: Welcome to 907 Teague Ave, situated on a quiet dead-end road east of Driggs, offering peaceful year-round comfort in a rustic-modern setting. The vaulted great room seamlessly connects to a spacious kitchen with rustic wood details and hardwood floors. This Idaho dream home features a walk-out basement, two-car garage, and one-acre fenced yard to accommodate your various needs. Free from covenants and HOA dues. Its versatility supports short or long-term rentals and allows for horses and other animals. Easy access to downtown Driggs and Ski-Hill Road, balances convenience with tranquility. Just 21 minutes from Grand Targhee Ski Resort and under an hour to Jackson Hole Mountain Resort, it embodies rural charm with modern amenities. The exterior siding, kitchen cabinets, and downstairs bathroom will be finished before closing.
